title: 16: I've Always had a Boyfriend ...
description: Sadie is one to always flaunt her HOT GIRL not summer but all four seasons. Well in her real personal life this isn't always the case. Episode 16 dives deep into the behind the scenes of Sadies boy life and how she really is never fully single like she says. Sadie also recaps her previous weekend at ROCK THE SOUTH where she met new TIKTOKERS and may or may not have a crush on them all.
